methods: abstract String getMethod() Gets the method associated with the request, for example "GET".
abstract Map<String, String> getRequestHeaders() Gets the headers associated with the request.
abstract Uri getUrl() Gets the URL for which the resource request was made.
abstract boolean hasGesture() Gets whether a gesture (such as a click) was associated with the request.
abstract boolean isForMainFrame() Gets whether the request was made for the main frame.
